import Vue from 'vue'
import App from './App.vue'
import store from "./store/index"
import {Row,Col,Menu,Submenu} from "element-ui"

Vue.use(Row)
Vue.use(Col)
Vue.use(Menu)
Vue.use(Submenu)


Vue.config.productionTip = false

new Vue({
  render: h => h(App),
  store
}).$mount('#app')
